premise_source_doc_sentence: Charles Lewis Haley  (  born January 6 , 1964  )  is a former American football linebacker and defensive end who played in the National Football League  (  NFL  )  for the San Francisco 49ers  (  1986 -- 1991 , 1998 -- 1999  )  and the Dallas Cowboys  (  1992 -- 1996  )  .
